<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 16:08:51 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/69f37e905c8dc</link><description>&lt;p&gt;外观。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="An old belfry reflected by a glass facade. " height="3419" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/69f37e905c8dc.jpg" width="1926"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 16:08:51 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>iOS 26锁屏：飞鸟与山景</title><link>https://some.pics/69f3416df3dd9</link><description>&lt;p&gt;运行iOS 26的iPhone锁屏截图。截图为单色，展现以一只飞鸟为中心的黑白场景，这只鸟在前方山脉与山谷远景的映衬下几乎全黑，山谷因大气逆温而被云雾遮蔽。利用iOS 26的一项功能，显示时间13:37的数字时钟下半部分被最远一排山脉局部遮挡。屏幕底部的快捷图标分别是手电筒（左侧）和相机应用Halide（右侧）。日期显示为“Do. 30. Apr.”，移动运营商为“Telekom.de”，电池电量为80%。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Screenshot of the lock screen on an iPhone running iOS 26. The screenshot is entirely monochrome showing a black and white scene centred on a bird in flight, the animal appearing almost completely black in front of a mountain and valley vista where the valley is obscured by clouds due to atmospheric inversion. Using a feature of iOS 26, the lower part of the digital clock face showing the time 13:37, is partly overlayed by the most distant row of mountains.  The quick access icons on the bottom of the screen are the flashlight (left) and the camera app Halide (right).  The date is shown as „Do. 30. Apr.“, the cellular provider as „Telekom.de“, and the battery is at 80%." height="2622" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/mangochutney/69f3416df3dd9.png" width="1206"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://mangochutney.some.pics"&gt;@mangochutney&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 11:53:19 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/69f30f7a9a36d</link><description>&lt;p&gt;晨光&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A brown leaf lying on its side in the grass. The sun, shining from the upper left corner, makes the dew from the night sparkle and the leaf almost transparent " height="2552" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/69f30f7a9a36d.jpg" width="3404"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 08:14:53 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/69f2ea371df3b</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Whaley在秋叶中嬉戏&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Whaley Autumn" height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/whaley/69f2ea371df3b.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://whaley.some.pics"&gt;@whaley&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 05:35:54 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>紧急提醒</title><link>https://some.pics/69f299ded821d</link><description>&lt;p&gt;🚨&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A small black and white dog lies in the grass with a blue sky behind her, and her ears are sticking up on high alert." height="2169" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/jinx/69f299ded821d.jpg" width="3858"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://jinx.some.pics"&gt;@jinx&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 23:53:05 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>